This layer combines information on polling districts, used to allocate polling stations at election times, with the location of the right polling station, thereby allowing for a search to be made on the address of an elector to direct them to the right location to cast their vote on election day.

It is updated around a month before an election at the same time as poll card information is produced

attributes.description:
Under Section 18A of the Representation of the People Act 1983 (as amended) the Council is required to divide each parliamentary constituency in the area into polling districts, to designate polling places for those polling districts

This layer shows Broxtowe's current polling stations. It is worth noting that because multiple polling districts may vote at one place, this layer may include multiple points for the same place.

attributes.description:
This layer combines information on polling districts, used to allocate polling stations at election times, with the location of the right polling station, thereby allowing for a search to be made on the address of an elector to direct them to the right location to cast their vote on election day.

It is updated around a month before an election at the same time as poll card information is produced

attributes.description:
This layer combines information on polling districts, used to allocate polling stations at election times, with the location of the right polling station, thereby allowing for a search to be made on the address of an elector to direct them to the right location to cast their vote on election day.

It is updated around a month before an election at the same time as poll card information is produced
